# 🛒 E-Commerce Web App Development Rules

## Project Overview

Build a modern, scalable, SEO-friendly eCommerce platform using Next.js with full responsive design, secure checkout, and admin management.

## Tech Stack Requirements

### Frontend

- **Framework**: Next.js (App Router only - no Pages Router)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS (primary) with CSS Modules when needed
- **State Management**: Zustand (preferred) or Redux Toolkit
- **Forms**: React Hook Form + Zod validation
- **UI Components**: ShadCN/UI components with Headless UI

### Backend

- **API**: Next.js API routes (no separate backend initially)
- **Database**: PostgreSQL with Prisma ORM
- **Authentication**: NextAuth.js / Auth.js
